05:45.570 --> 05:49.020
a lot of dependencies on third-party vendors,

05:49.020 --> 05:50.460
and generally speaking,

05:50.460 --> 05:53.550
are under-resourced and under-prepared

05:53.550 --> 05:57.810
when it comes to their cybersecurity defenses.

