06:40.080 --> 06:42.630
just because of the level of investment,

06:42.630 --> 06:46.380
the sophistication that goes into their controls.

06:46.380 --> 06:49.350
So I would say that's one of the better,

06:49.350 --> 06:51.570
stronger ends of the spectrum.

06:51.570 --> 06:55.500
