13:50.400 --> 13:53.940
into that communications process, and protocol,

13:53.940 --> 13:58.140
and practicing what it's like to move a couple of inquiries

13:58.140 --> 14:01.530
from one stage gate to another,

14:01.530 --> 14:05.760
I think can be worth its weight all day every day

14:05.760 --> 14:08.820
